                        <li><strong>Analytics:</strong> To generate reports, analyse usage patterns, and improve service quality</li>
                        <li><strong>Security:</strong> To detect fraud, prevent unauthorised access, and ensure platform security</li>
                        <li><strong>Legal compliance:</strong> To comply with applicable laws, regulations, and legal processes</li>
